Spherical Zebra Approximation

--Code--

ang = seq(0,360/32*2,length=33)[-1]
for(i in 1:32) {
sphere(r=0.45,angle=c(0,ang[i],0),material=light(intensity=1,image_texture = array(c(1,0,1,0),dim=c(32,32,4)))) %>% render_scene(lookfrom=c(0,10,10),fov=0)
}
